Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:07.92,2,,0,0,0,,Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:09.88,2,,0,0,0,,Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.31,0:00:11.68,2,,0,0,0,,Air.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:13.52,2,,0,0,0,,Water.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.21,0:00:18.83,2,,0,0,0,,Only the Avatar can master all four elements
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.21,0:00:21.01,2,,0,0,0,,and bring balance to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,土强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,火烈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.31,0:00:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,气和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,水善
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.21,0:00:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,只有神通能掌握所有四种元素
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.21,0:00:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,并为世界带来平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.01,0:00:27.04,3,,0,0,0,,{\fs200\t(0,200,0.5,\fs30)\pos(363,391)}{\fad(0,200)}降世神通：科拉传奇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:30.03,2,,0,0,0,,Unalaq has forced Korra into opening the northern portal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:31.76,2,,0,0,0,,and trapped Jinora in the spirit world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.13,0:00:33.48,2,,0,0,0,,Back in Republic City,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.48,0:00:35.48,2,,0,0,0,,everybody loves Varrick's Nuktuk movers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.81,0:00:37.50,2,,0,0,0,,Everybody, that is, except Mako,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:39.66,2,,0,0,0,,whose pursuit of Varrick has landed him in the slammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.03,0:00:41.39,2,,0,0,0,,And in the Southern water tribe,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:43.93,2,,0,0,0,,Unalaq's army is nearing victory in the civil war.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:46.84,2,,0,0,0,,But Tonraq isn't about to give up without a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,吴纳克强迫科拉打开北极大门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,把吉诺拉困在灵界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.13,0:00:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,回到共和城
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.48,0:00:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人都喜欢瓦里克的纳塔克系列电影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.81,0:00:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人，除了信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,对瓦里克进行追查，结果他被整进监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.03,0:00:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,南极水族这边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,吴纳克的军队在内战中就要胜利了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但托纳克非战不屈
