Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:51.07,3,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\2c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(361.044,364.011)}{\fad(1600,600)}第十一集：繁星之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.73,0:01:08.35,2,,0,0,0,,Where's Jinora?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.58,0:01:13.95,2,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.49,0:01:19.83,2,,0,0,0,,Her spirit is trapped in the spirit world,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.28,0:01:21.78,2,,0,0,0,,but she's going to be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:24.05,2,,0,0,0,,How could this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:25.34,2,,0,0,0,,It was all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:28.90,2,,0,0,0,,I should have never let Jinora enter the spirit world without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.97,0:01:29.93,2,,0,0,0,,I couldn't protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.33,0:01:31.80,2,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Pema.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.06,0:01:34.31,2,,0,0,0,,I tried to save her, but Unalaq tricked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.58,0:01:35.32,2,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, honey,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.73,0:01:39.10,2,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to stop until our little girl is back safe with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.92,0:01:47.89,2,,0,0,0,,You've got a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.19,0:01:50.11,2,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mako.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.32,0:01:50.62,2,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:52.71,2,,0,0,0,,What's with the fancy duds?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:56.34,2,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way to the big finale for <i>Nuktuk: Hero of the South.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.69,0:01:57.97,2,,0,0,0,,Yeah, everyone's gonna be there,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.21,0:02:00.18,2,,0,0,0,,except for, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.42,0:02:01.06,2,,0,0,0,,you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:03.33,2,,0,0,0,,Because you're in jail and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:04.69,2,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the reminder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.07,0:02:06.12,2,,0,0,0,,Hey, I brought you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:08.00,2,,0,0,0,,I thought this would brighten up your new place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.24,0:02:08.99,2,,0,0,0,,Read the inscription.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:13.23,2,,0,0,0,,"Dear Mako, Nuktuk says, 'keep smiling.'"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.18,0:02:16.87,2,,0,0,0,,did you come by just to give me a poster?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.09,0:02:18.76,2,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.59,0:02:23.69,2,,0,0,0,,I came by to give you my sincere, heartfelt words of encouragement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.38,0:02:26.74,2,,0,0,0,,I know our lives have been moving in two different directions,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:29.48,2,,0,0,0,,but I want you to know that I will always be there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:31.40,2,,0,0,0,,We are brothers, after all,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:34.36,2,,0,0,0,,even if one of us is a member of high society and the other one is a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.64,0:02:35.68,2,,0,0,0,,I am not a criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.93,0:02:37.45,2,,0,0,0,,Of course I know that,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:39.62,2,,0,0,0,,but you do kinda look like one,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.65,0:02:42.34,2,,0,0,0,,'cause you're in a jail, and that's where criminals live.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:43.29,2,,0,0,0,,I was set up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:47.70,2,,0,0,0,,Varrick knew I had figured out he was hiring gangsters to pose as northern soldiers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:49.77,2,,0,0,0,,to get Republic City to join the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:51.81,2,,0,0,0,,That's why he had me arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.70,0:02:56.25,2,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see what you're doing. You're going for the insanity defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.45,0:02:57.07,2,,0,0,0,,Smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:02:57.83,2,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:03:00.70,2,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to tell you that Varrick isn't what he seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:02.96,2,,0,0,0,,Where's Asami? She'll listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:05.43,2,,0,0,0,,I asked her to come, but she said it was too hard for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:07.11,2,,0,0,0,,You being in jail like this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:09.11,2,,0,0,0,,reminds her of her dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:11.52,2,,0,0,0,,Okay, gotta run,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:12.65,2,,0,0,0,,but I'll be back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:16.39,2,,0,0,0,,And I am gonna get you the best attorney fame and fortune can buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.04,0:03:18.01,2,,0,0,0,,Bolin, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:20.18,2,,0,0,0,,If my theory about Varrick is right,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:22.60,2,,0,0,0,,something might go down tonight at your premiere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:24.43,2,,0,0,0,,Promise me you'll keep your eyes peeled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:26.13,2,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay, big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:27.31,2,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:31.54,2,,0,0,0,,That insanity defense is definitely gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:38.37,2,,0,0,0,,Should we wait another day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:40.82,2,,0,0,0,,Korra still might come with reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:42.30,2,,0,0,0,,We can't wait any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:45.41,2,,0,0,0,,It's time we take back what is ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:47.71,2,,0,0,0,,It's time to take back our city!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.86,0:03:50.09,2,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:12.27,2,,0,0,0,,Say "Nuktuk."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:17.75,2,,0,0,0,,There they are, folks,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:19.33,2,,0,0,0,,the sweethearts of the big screen,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:22.40,2,,0,0,0,,and Republic City's most famous couple,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:24.81,2,,0,0,0,,Bolin and ginger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:26.46,2,,0,0,0,,Let me get a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,让我拍张照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.92,0:04:30.13,2,,0,0,0,,Wow, that was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:31.30,2,,0,0,0,,And did you hear what Shiro said?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:33.71,2,,0,0,0,,We're Republic City's most famous couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:35.14,2,,0,0,0,,Bolin, you're a doll,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:38.30,2,,0,0,0,,but you're as dumb as the rocks you bend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:40.30,2,,0,0,0,,We are not a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:42.12,2,,0,0,0,,That's not what Shiro said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:49.21,2,,0,0,0,,Stop stuffing your moustaches with varri-cakes and get to your post!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:50.22,2,,0,0,0,,You got it, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:53.12,2,,0,0,0,,You two are the pinnacle of refinement.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:56.85,2,,0,0,0,,This star-studded event just keeps getting star-studdier, folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:05:00.35,2,,0,0,0,,President Raiko and the first lady, Buttercup Raiko, just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:03.67,2,,0,0,0,,And they're being greeted by entrepreneur extraordinaire,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:04.49,2,,0,0,0,,Varrick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:08.03,2,,0,0,0,,There they are, my two most honored guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:10.03,2,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:11.97,2,,0,0,0,,No expense has been spared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:15.11,2,,0,0,0,,I brought in the finest entertainers from Ba Sing Se
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.11,0:05:16.90,2,,0,0,0,,and the best food from around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:20.17,2,,0,0,0,,Heck, I even had this red carpet imported from the fire nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:23.24,2,,0,0,0,,They make the best red stuff over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:26.26,2,,0,0,0,,In fact... all right, picture time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.92,0:05:30.36,2,,0,0,0,,Varrick, you didn't have to do all this for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:31.79,2,,0,0,0,,I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:34.80,2,,0,0,0,,Mr. President, I took one look at your wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:38.53,2,,0,0,0,,and I knew that you were a man of exquisite taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:41.78,2,,0,0,0,,And that's why I know you're gonna love this mover!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:43.61,2,,0,0,0,,Varrick, I know what you're doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:48.60,2,,0,0,0,,and I doubt your propaganda is going to change my mind about going to war with the northern water tribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:52.75,2,,0,0,0,,Oh, I think you'll be surprised how persuasive I can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:12.25,2,,0,0,0,,Thank you all for coming to the finale of <i>Nuktuk: Hero of the South.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:14.86,2,,0,0,0,,You know, when I first started this project,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:17.14,2,,0,0,0,,there were a lot of naysayers out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:19.65,2,,0,0,0,,"You can't make pictures move," they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:23.67,2,,0,0,0,,"You can't take some knucklehead earthbender and make him a star," they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:27.25,2,,0,0,0,,"You can't teach a polar bear dog to speak," they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:29.90,2,,0,0,0,,Well, they're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:32.03,2,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the magic of the movers,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:34.50,2,,0,0,0,,our furry friends have found their voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:38.23,2,,0,0,0,,And you'll be shocked to hear what they have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:43.29,2,,0,0,0,,They speak of the injustice that's happening in the Southern water tribe right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:46.55,2,,0,0,0,,My hope is that their words
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:48.35,2,,0,0,0,,and this epic mover
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:52.89,2,,0,0,0,,will inspire a real-life hero to rise up and help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:56.28,2,,0,0,0,,Thank you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:06:58.28,2,,0,0,0,,Enjoy the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:06.19,2,,0,0,0,,When last we left our hero, be was captured by the evil Unalaq's dastardly pet bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.58,0:07:10.04,2,,0,0,0,,Amazingly, with the power of his whistling, Nuktuk escaped...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.92,0:07:17.21,2,,0,0,0,,And decided to seek out counsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:21.26,2,,0,0,0,,Thank you, wise sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:23.44,2,,0,0,0,,I will travel to Republic City and seek help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:28.97,2,,0,0,0,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:31.55,2,,0,0,0,,I'm just working on a cure for the common cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:34.93,2,,0,0,0,,No longer will my citizens suffer from the sniffles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:38.36,2,,0,0,0,,Mr. President, there's something more important than the sniffles right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:41.31,2,,0,0,0,,I need your help to stop the evil Unalaq.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:43.10,2,,0,0,0,,Did you say "help"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:47.17,2,,0,0,0,,If there is one thing I love doing, it's helping people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:50.02,2,,0,0,0,,The seal line seemed a bit far-fetched,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.02,0:07:53.23,2,,0,0,0,,but the portrayal of this president is right on the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:07:58.37,2,,0,0,0,,I think this is your best mover yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.31,2,,0,0,0,,I just wish Mako was here to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:22.33,2,,0,0,0,,I like to eat the top off the varri-cake first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:25.57,2,,0,0,0,,I just try to shove the whole thing in my mouth at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.55,2,,0,0,0,,I love our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:50.51,2,,0,0,0,,Northern water tribe automatons!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.32,2,,0,0,0,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:56.97,2,,0,0,0,,Nuktuk cannot stop Unalaq.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:08:59.07,2,,0,0,0,,Must destroy Nuktuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.79,0:09:16.84,2,,0,0,0,,Looks like you forgot that water and automatons don't mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:22.33,2,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, circuits not working.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:25.34,2,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:26.28,2,,0,0,0,,But wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:28.09,2,,0,0,0,,Where's Juji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:31.72,2,,0,0,0,,Nukno!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:34.84,2,,0,0,0,,You can't die, Juji.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:36.98,2,,0,0,0,,Not on my watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.90,0:09:40.38,2,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Nuktuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:42.97,2,,0,0,0,,At least I got to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:46.45,2,,0,0,0,,Your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:53.17,2,,0,0,0,,Juji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:05.95,2,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:08.65,2,,0,0,0,,It seems like this mover is really getting to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:11.22,2,,0,0,0,,You do know Juji's not really dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.49,0:10:13.80,2,,0,0,0,,Of course I know. Juji's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:18.00,2,,0,0,0,,He comes back to life in the end when the doomsday device shifts the polarity of the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.62,0:10:20.00,2,,0,0,0,,Oops. Spoiler.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:21.04,2,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:22.51,2,,0,0,0,,Then what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:24.95,2,,0,0,0,,I guess I just miss my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:28.29,2,,0,0,0,,Everything is going so well for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:30.86,2,,0,0,0,,but it feels empty without everyone around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.74,0:10:34.46,2,,0,0,0,,Korra's gone, Mako's in jail, you're doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:36.31,2,,0,0,0,,Business lady stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:38.86,2,,0,0,0,,Team Avatar's fallen apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:40.36,2,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:44.02,2,,0,0,0,,Things have changed so much since we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.03,0:10:48.48,2,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come back in and fish watching the mover with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.74,0:10:49.35,2,,0,0,0,,You go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:51.35,2,,0,0,0,,I need another minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:00.56,2,,0,0,0,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:25.18,2,,0,0,0,,They're after the president!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:32.49,2,,0,0,0,,You're too late, Nuktuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:37.56,2,,0,0,0,,Soon, my doomsday device will shoot this block of ice into the earth's core,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.79,0:11:39.88,2,,0,0,0,,freezing the entire planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:44.20,2,,0,0,0,,And I will be the ruler of ice earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:49.59,2,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:55.60,2,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:13.82,2,,0,0,0,,Mr. President, get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:14.79,2,,0,0,0,,I'm here to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:28.72,2,,0,0,0,,Looks like there's nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:38.17,2,,0,0,0,,Secure the president and call for backup immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:57.65,2,,0,0,0,,Nuktuk, Bolin, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:14.99,2,,0,0,0,,This is unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.22,0:13:18.19,2,,0,0,0,,Bolin is bending two full stacks of earth discs at once,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:20.10,2,,0,0,0,,which would normally be illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:22.77,2,,0,0,0,,But then again, he's fighting three waterbenders,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:24.63,2,,0,0,0,,so all rules are out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:42.14,2,,0,0,0,,Tell me who sent you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:44.59,2,,0,0,0,,It was Varrick. Please don't hurt me, Nuktuk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:52.25,2,,0,0,0,,I think this is our cue to exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:54.55,2,,0,0,0,,Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:04.94,2,,0,0,0,,It's a knockout!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.35,0:14:23.53,2,,0,0,0,,They're falling back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:47.21,2,,0,0,0,,Varrick's plan was to kidnap you and blame it on the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:51.77,2,,0,0,0,,Then Republic City would have no choice but to join the war on the side of the South.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:54.04,2,,0,0,0,,I can't believe Varrick would do something like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:55.49,2,,0,0,0,,and no one saw it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:14:57.00,2,,0,0,0,,Actually, someone did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.57,0:14:58.45,2,,0,0,0,,Remember Mako?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.05,0:15:01.65,2,,0,0,0,,You've got a great officer on your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.07,0:15:03.19,2,,0,0,0,,He's one of the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:11.67,2,,0,0,0,,I can't believe my boyfriend is a real-life hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:13.33,2,,0,0,0,,Boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:16.51,2,,0,0,0,,Wait, stop. I thought you said we <i>weren't</i> a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.28,0:15:20.93,2,,0,0,0,,You really are as dumb as those rocks. Of course we're a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:23.77,2,,0,0,0,,Bolin, you saved the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.93,0:15:26.00,2,,0,0,0,,And you proved Mako was right all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:27.53,2,,0,0,0,,We have to go tell him what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:28.04,2,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:31.01,2,,0,0,0,,Oh, you meant right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:36.96,2,,0,0,0,,President Raiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:39.32,2,,0,0,0,,Avatar Korra, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:41.69,2,,0,0,0,,Sir, I know I've asked for your help before,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.17,2,,0,0,0,,but things have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:46.45,2,,0,0,0,,Unalaq doesn't just want to take over the South anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:49.35,2,,0,0,0,,He wants to destroy the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:57.39,2,,0,0,0,,Unalaq is gonna destroy the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:15:59.74,2,,0,0,0,,He really does have a doomsday device?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:04.61,2,,0,0,0,,He's trying to release a powerful dark spirit during harmonic convergence, which is only a few days away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:06.24,2,,0,0,0,,If he succeeds,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:09.01,2,,0,0,0,,the world as we know it is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:11.44,2,,0,0,0,,Sir, we desperately need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:16.20,2,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Korra, but my answer is still no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:20.09,2,,0,0,0,,There are lives on the line! And my daughter is one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:21.77,2,,0,0,0,,Raiko, you must reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.95,0:16:24.52,2,,0,0,0,,I'm aware that lives are on the line,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:27.14,2,,0,0,0,,and that's precisely why my troops are staying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:29.98,2,,0,0,0,,If the world is going to be thrown into chaos, like you claim,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:31.93,2,,0,0,0,,I need to protect my citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:32.88,2,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:35.08,2,,0,0,0,,Sir. Nuktuk needs your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:37.54,2,,0,0,0,,I know you love helping people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:42.27,2,,0,0,0,,Son, I appreciate you saving my life, and I'm a big fan of your work,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:44.27,2,,0,0,0,,but my decision is final.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:48.67,2,,0,0,0,,I never should have saved that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:50.86,2,,0,0,0,,If you guys need help, I'm here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.18,0:16:52.10,2,,0,0,0,,Yeah, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.27,0:16:55.14,2,,0,0,0,,Thank you. It's so good to see you guys again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:57.68,2,,0,0,0,,Wait, where's Mako?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:04.67,2,,0,0,0,,So how was the big premiere?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:07.77,2,,0,0,0,,I saved the president! In real life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:09.16,2,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:12.51,2,,0,0,0,,You were right about Varrick. He tried to kidnap Raiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:13.84,2,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:16.75,2,,0,0,0,,But it didn't work, because of you. And because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:20.17,2,,0,0,0,,Let's just say we both did good. Beifong says you're free to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:24.19,2,,0,0,0,,Sorry for ever doubting you, Mako.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:25.29,2,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:40.20,2,,0,0,0,,Nice job, Mako. You're going to make a great Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:43.47,2,,0,0,0,,But, chief, there aren't any Detective openings right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:45.72,2,,0,0,0,,Actually, we have two openings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:56.39,2,,0,0,0,,Mako, I missed you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:03.64,2,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, did I forget to tell you? Korra's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:04.53,2,,0,0,0,,Korra,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:06.41,2,,0,0,0,,hey, I missed you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:08.80,2,,0,0,0,,So you're not still mad at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:09.97,2,,0,0,0,,Why would I be mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:14.24,2,,0,0,0,,We had that fight before you left, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:16.81,2,,0,0,0,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:19.15,2,,0,0,0,,I got attacked by a dark spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:20.91,2,,0,0,0,,and I lost my memory for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:23.08,2,,0,0,0,,Maybe it hasn't all come back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.15,0:18:25.17,2,,0,0,0,,Was it a bad fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:33.73,2,,0,0,0,,No. No, it... it wasn't that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:41.43,2,,0,0,0,,Korra, we don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:44.41,2,,0,0,0,,We need to figure out how to deal with Unalaq.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.69,0:18:46.95,2,,0,0,0,,I think I know just the man to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:51.47,2,,0,0,0,,Guys, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:54.35,2,,0,0,0,,What do you think? Varrick industries built this prison,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.56,0:18:56.49,2,,0,0,0,,and I had this cell made special.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:58.66,2,,0,0,0,,I had a feeling I'd end up here one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:02.07,2,,0,0,0,,Zhu Li, come on! We got guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:04.44,2,,0,0,0,,Whip up a pot of that green tea I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:05.23,2,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:07.66,2,,0,0,0,,Zhu Li's in prison with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:10.84,2,,0,0,0,,Of course. I don't go anywhere without my assistant. Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:13.74,2,,0,0,0,,We're not interested in your tea, and this isn't a friendly visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.01,0:19:16.88,2,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you guys are still mad about everything that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:19.09,2,,0,0,0,,I did some good things too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:21.75,2,,0,0,0,,Korra, who warned you about Unalaq?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:22.73,2,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.17,0:19:25.47,2,,0,0,0,,Bolin, who got you into the movers?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:26.26,2,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:28.72,2,,0,0,0,,Asami, who saved your company?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.05,0:19:29.59,2,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:32.15,2,,0,0,0,,Mako, who got you thrown in jail?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:33.00,2,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:35.00,2,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, I guess that was a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:38.48,2,,0,0,0,,You stole everything from me, and you tried to kidnap the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:39.63,2,,0,0,0,,Those are pretty bad too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:41.34,2,,0,0,0,,I wasn't going to hurt him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:43.34,2,,0,0,0,,I just needed to start a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.67,0:19:44.61,2,,0,0,0,,Well, a bigger war.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.09,0:19:47.84,2,,0,0,0,,Well, we're gonna end it. Where's all the stuff you stole from Asami?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:50.56,2,,0,0,0,,The future industries stuff? It's on my battleship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:52.15,2,,0,0,0,,You have a battleship?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:53.61,2,,0,0,0,,Of course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:55.61,2,,0,0,0,,I bought the first one they made,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.36,0:19:57.94,2,,0,0,0,,named her the <i>Zhu Li.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:01.45,2,,0,0,0,,You named your battleship after your assistant?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:05.15,2,,0,0,0,,Yep. They're both cold, heartless war machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:07.15,2,,0,0,0,,Your tea, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.59,0:20:11.16,2,,0,0,0,,Look, I am truly sorry for the mess I caused.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:12.65,2,,0,0,0,,Let me make it up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:14.06,2,,0,0,0,,Take <i>Zhu Li.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.83,0:20:18.59,2,,0,0,0,,My battleship, it's yours, and everything on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:22.70,2,,0,0,0,,It's not the fleet we were looking for, but it's the next best thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.85,0:20:26.26,2,,0,0,0,,All right! Team Avatar is back in business!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:35.78,2,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.47,0:20:39.27,2,,0,0,0,,We're gonna stop Unalaq and get Jinora back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:41.32,2,,0,0,0,,I hope my dad's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:45.12,2,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:03.20,2,,0,0,0,,Get the men and fall back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:04.48,2,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:12.58,2,,0,0,0,,I'm going to end this right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:13.79,2,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:27.03,2,,0,0,0,,Hello, Tonraq.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.30,0:21:28.42,2,,0,0,0,,Looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.59,0:21:41.99,2,,0,0,0,,Brother, I'm too strong for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:43.63,2,,0,0,0,,You're no brother of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.00,0:21:44.76,2,,0,0,0,,You betrayed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:46.39,2,,0,0,0,,You had me banished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.48,0:21:48.20,2,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:55.32,2,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.40,0:21:57.36,2,,0,0,0,,He's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.93,0:22:00.78,2,,0,0,0,,You are not the true chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:01.72,2,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.86,0:22:04.42,2,,0,0,0,,And you will bow to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.04,0:23:09.49,2,,0,0,0,,Now that I've defeated you,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.27,0:23:11.89,2,,0,0,0,,your daughter is next.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.86,0:01:00.73,2,,0,0,0,,Dad's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.86,0:01:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.73,0:01:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,吉诺拉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.58,0:01:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.49,0:01:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,她的魂魄被困在灵界了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.28,0:01:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但她不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,全是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不该让吉诺拉没有我陪伴就进入灵界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.97,0:01:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我没能保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.33,0:01:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉，姵玛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.06,0:01:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我想救她，可是吴纳克骗了我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.58,0:01:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心，亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.73,0:01:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们的女儿回来前，我不会停手的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.92,0:01:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,有人探监
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.19,0:01:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨，信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.32,0:01:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛穿那么花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我准备去《纳塔克：南方英雄》的终场呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.69,0:01:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.21,0:02:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,只是缺了……嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.42,0:02:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,缺你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你在蹲监狱什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢提醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.07,0:02:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，我有东西给你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定能让你好好装扮一下这
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.24,0:02:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你读读
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的信，纳塔克说，要保持笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.18,0:02:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你来这里就为了给我张海报？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.09,0:02:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.59,0:02:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我来是给你我最真挚的，发自内心的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.38,0:02:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我们的生活踏上了两条不同的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但我要你知道我永远会支持你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟，我们是兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕我们一个入了上流社会，另一个成了罪犯，也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.64,0:02:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.93,0:02:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然知道你不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可是你长得确实像罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.65,0:02:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你在监狱里，监狱又是关罪犯的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我是被算计了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦里克知道我看破了他雇佣黑社会装成北方士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,想让共和城加入战争的技俩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他把我抓起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.70,0:02:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，我明白你在做什么了，你“精神失常”了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.45,0:02:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,真有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:02:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:03:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我是要告诉你瓦里克肚里没安好心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,麻美呢，她会听懂我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我让她也同来，可是她说，这对她太难受了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样蹲监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,让她想起她爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但明天我会还来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我要给你请来我请得起的最好的律师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.04,0:03:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,波林，等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我对瓦里克的推测没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,今天你的终场上肯定会出大事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你得保证，得多留个心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，行行行，老大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,“精神失常”这招绝对奏效
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要再等一天么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,科拉仍然有可能带着援兵回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能再等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们得夺回属于我们的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是夺回我们城市的时刻了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.86,0:03:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,然也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,说纳塔克
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,各位，他们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,荧幕上的小俩口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,也是共和城最出名的一对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,波林和小姜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.92,0:04:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,喔，真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你听到四郎说什么了没
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是共和城最出名的一对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,波林，你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你脑子笨得像你御的石头一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可不是一对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,四郎可没那么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你别再往嘴里填蛋糕了，快去站岗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命，长官
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩可真是人上人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,各位，群星荟萃的大会又有明星加入了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:05:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,雷鼓总统和第一夫人雷鼓毛茛刚刚驾临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,迎接他们的是杰出企业家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦里克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,您二位贵宾终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,预算我一点都没省
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我请来了永固城最好的演员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.11,0:05:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,弄来了各地最好的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,哈，我还从火烈国进口了这条红地毯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他们造的红色东西那是顶呱呱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,其实吧…好，来合个影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.92,0:05:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦里克，你不需要为我们做这些的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,总统大人，一见到您的夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道您是一位品味上流的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我知道您肯定会喜欢这电影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦里克，我知道你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我看你的宣传作秀是不会打动我和北方水族部落开战的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，我的说服力会让您刮目相看的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢各位来观看《纳塔克：南方英雄》的终场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,其实，在我刚开始这个企划的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,反对者相当的多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说“你怎么可能让画面动起来”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说“你不可能让那个笨蛋御土师成为明星”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还说“你不可能让极熊狗会说话，”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，他们都错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏这电影的神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们毛茸茸的小家伙也会说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要说的话，会让你们大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他们所说的是，在南方水族部落正发生的不义之举
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望他们的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这部史诗般的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,会让现实中诞生一位英雄揭竿而起，拔刀相助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:06:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,请看电影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,上回我们说到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的英雄被邪恶的吴纳克那卑鄙的宠物鸟抓走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.58,0:07:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但不可思议的是，凭着口哨功夫，纳塔克逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.92,0:07:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,然后决心去寻求议会的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你，贤者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我这就去共和城请求救兵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在研究流感的解药呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我的市民们不久再也不会受鼻塞之苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,总统先生，现在有件事比鼻塞更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要您帮忙阻止邪恶的吴纳克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你说帮忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有什么东西我喜欢做，那肯定就是帮人一把了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这台词虽然有点牵强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这位总统的形象还真像回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:07:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉这是你目前最棒的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我真希望信也能来看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢先吃瓦里牌蛋糕的上面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我嘛就一口吞下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱我们的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,北方水族机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,纳塔克无法阻止吴纳克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:08:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,必须消灭纳塔克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.79,0:09:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你好像忘了机器人不能碰到水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不！电路无法工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不过等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,朱吉在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,朱吉你不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要亲眼看着你死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.90,0:09:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的，纳塔克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,至少，我曾做过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,朱吉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来你好像真的入戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该知道朱吉并没有真正死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.49,0:10:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然知道他还好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,当吴纳克的末日武装倒转地球磁极的时候，他复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.62,0:10:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，剧透了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,可能我是想念我的朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在一帆风顺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,然而没有大家的陪伴，我心里空落落的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.74,0:10:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,科拉走了，马克入狱了，而你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,现在忙于商务
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,神通小队已经支离破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,自我们相遇以来，世事变化巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.03,0:10:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么不进来和我一起看完这电影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.74,0:10:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己再待会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是冲着总统来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你来得太迟了纳塔克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,很快，我的末日武装将会把这块寒冰射入地核
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.79,0:11:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,冰冻整个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而我，将会成为冰雪世界的主宰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我不这样认为
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我不这样认为
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,总统先生，退到后面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我是来救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你们已经无路可走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,立刻联系后援，保护总统
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,波林（纳塔克）小心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这简直难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.22,0:13:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,波林同时御着两叠全部的土盘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这在平时是犯规的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不过，他正在独力和三名水宗对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,所以还管他什么规定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我是谁指使你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是瓦里克，请不要伤害我，纳塔克
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们该跑路了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为你还去得了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,击倒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.35,0:14:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他们撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦里克的计划是绑架你然后把帐算到北极水族头上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那样，共和城将别无选择，只能与南方并肩作战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我不敢相信瓦里克居然能做出这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,而且竟然没人识破他的诡计
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:14:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上有人识破了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.57,0:14:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,还记得信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.05,0:15:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你有一名很好的警员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.07,0:15:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他是最棒的警官之一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我不敢相信，我的男友在现实生活中竟然也是英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,男友？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，我想你说过我们不是一对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.28,0:15:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是和那堆石头一样木讷，我们当然是一对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,波林你救下了总统
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.93,0:15:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你证明了信的清白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得告诉他事情经过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,噢，你是说现在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,雷鼓总统
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,神通科拉，怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,先生，我知道我之前就已经向您提过请求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在情况不同
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,吴纳克不止想要占领水族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他还想要毁灭整个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,吴纳克要毁灭世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:15:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他真有末日武装吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他准备在几天后的谐波汇聚时，释放一只强大的黑暗神灵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在认识的世界就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,先生，我们急需你的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉科拉，我依旧只能说不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我的女儿和很多其他人已经命悬一线了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,雷鼓，我必须请你三思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.95,0:16:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道很多人有性命危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是我的部队一直得留在这里的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这个世界如你们所说将要陷入混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要保护我的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,先生，纳塔克需要你的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你喜欢帮助别人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子，我感谢你救了我的命，你的作品也很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我意已决
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我真不该救他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你们需要帮助的话，有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.18,0:16:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，我也在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.27,0:16:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢，能再次与你们相聚真好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你那隆重的首秀怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我救了总统！可不是在戏里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你对瓦里克的看法是正确的，他想绑架雷鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这个计划失败了，因为有我们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，就算我们都有功劳，北方警长说你可以走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,信，当时怀疑你真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟，别放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,信，干得好，你会成为名侦探的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但是警长，现在警探部门没有空缺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我刚刚找到了两个空缺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,信，我太想念你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，我是不是忘记告诉你了，科拉回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,科拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，我也想你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你不生我气了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我为什么要生气呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你走之前我们吵了一架，还记得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不，记不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我之后被一个黑暗神灵袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那段时间失忆了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,也许还没完全恢复吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.15,0:18:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那次争吵得厉害吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不，不，没那么糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,科拉，我们没有多少时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得想出对付吴纳克的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.69,0:18:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我应该知道现在需要谁了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们，嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样，瓦里克重工建造了这个监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.56,0:18:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我给这个牢房做了些特殊的打点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,看来我今儿得在这里过上一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,朱莉，快来，我们有客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,快沏上一壶我最喜欢的那种绿茶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,朱莉和你一起坐牢么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，我去哪都要带上我的助理，你们还不知道么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们对你的茶没兴趣，而且我们不是来探监的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.01,0:19:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,别告诉我你们还在为那些发生过的事生气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我也干过好事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,科拉，是谁警告你吴纳克没安好心的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.17,0:19:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,波林，是谁让你演那部电影的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,麻美，是谁拯救了你的公司？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.05,0:19:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,诚哥，是谁让你蹲了监狱？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,还是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，对了，好像那不是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你夺走了我的一切，而且你试图绑架总统
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那些也是坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想伤害他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想引发战争
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.67,0:19:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一场大战
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.09,0:19:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要结束这场战争，你从麻美那都偷了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,未来实业的那些？都在我的战列舰上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你居然有战列舰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,当然有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他们造的第一艘我就买下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.36,0:19:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,她的舰名是：朱莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你用你的助理命名战列舰么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,对，她们都是冷血无情的战争机器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,先生，茶好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.59,0:20:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说吧，我对我造成的烂摊子表示抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我就来补偿你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,朱莉归你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.83,0:20:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是朱莉号，上面所有的东西也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不是我们想要的船，但这其实也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.85,0:20:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好！神通小组重新启航了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.47,0:20:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一定能阻止吴纳克并救回吉诺拉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望我父亲没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定他没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,带上他们撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在就来解决这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊托纳克
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.30,0:21:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是来找我的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.59,0:21:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥，我比你强太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本不是我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.00,0:21:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你背叛了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是你把我流放走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.48,0:21:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.40,0:21:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我的猎物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.93,0:22:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是真正的族长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.86,0:22:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你还不赶紧给我鞠躬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.04,0:23:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我打倒你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.27,0:23:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,下一个就轮到你女儿了
